{"type":"message","id":"80421ae4","parentId":"033ace36","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:52:43.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has bought 10 shares of BABA. According to MEMORY.md, I need to act as a \"trading supervisor\" and review trades against the rules. Let me check the trading rules and current context.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md:\n**交易红线**\n1. 不做日内交易\n2. 不做空美股\n3. 不碰衍生品\n4. 不融资杠杆\n5. 不市价交易（必须挂单）\n\n**买入规则**: 禁止: 52周>70%、PE>35、单仓>1%、总趋势>20% | 必须: 限价单+技术位\n\n**卖出规则**: 禁止: 亏损<10%卖出、持仓<30天 | 必须: 亏损>15%止损、盈利>50%分批止盈\n\n**情绪控制**: 亏损后24h不开仓、冲动等10分钟、22:00后不交易\n\nCurrent portfolio shows they have:\n- ORCL: 200股 (趋势仓位)\n- NVDA: 100股 (趋势仓位)\n- AMZN: 10股 (1%)\n- 短期国债: 68%\n- 现金: 1%\n\nThe user bought BABA without going through the AI review process. I need to review this trade post-facto. According to MEMORY.md, the AI should review trades when the user says \"审查交易\" → AI checks rules → outputs 通过/警告/阻止.\n\nSince this already happened, I should:\n1. Note the violation (trading at night 09:52 GMT+8 = 21:52, which is past 22:00 but close)\n2. Review if this was a limit order or market order\n3. Check if this follows the portfolio rules\n\nI need to ask for details about the trade to properly review it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.memory_search:0","name":"memory_search","arguments":{"query":"BABA 阿里巴巴 交易规则"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":10020,"output":398,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10418,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771984355455}}
