{"type":"message","id":"bce9b391","parentId":"974a4c1c","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:52:49.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Memory search failed due to API issues, but I have the MEMORY.md content in the context. The user bought BABA at 09:52 GMT+8 (which is 21:52 local time). According to the rules:\n\n- **不市价交易 (必须挂单)**\n- **22:00后不交易** - This is 21:52, so technically before 22:00, but very close\n- **单仓>1%** - Need to check if BABA position exceeds 1% of portfolio\n\nAccording to MEMORY.md, the user is @worldhello321 and I'm a \"投资伙伴 + 交易监督员\". I need to review this trade.\n\nThe user says \"看来又出了点问题\" which suggests they might have broken a rule. Let me do a proper trade review.\n\nI should:\n1. Acknowledge the trade\n2. Ask for details (price, order type) if needed\n3. Review against rules\n4. Add BABA to the portfolio tracking\n\nLet me do a review based on what I know.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>收到，你需要审查这笔 BABA 交易。⚠️\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 交易审查：BABA (10股)\n\n| 规则 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **限价单？** | ❓待确认 | 是挂单还是市价买入？ |\n| **单仓≤1%** | ⚠️风险 | 当前持仓：ORCL+NVDA约30%，AMZN 1%。加BABA后需确认总趋势仓位是否超限 |\n| **22:00后禁交易** | ⚠️边缘 | 交易时间 21:52，仅提前8分钟 |\n| **52周位置<70%** | ❓待查 | 需要当前股价判断 |\n| **PE<35** | ❓待查 | |\n\n---\n\n**请确认：**\n1. **买入价格**？（是否为限价单）\n2. **为何在此时买入？** 是计划内还是冲动交易？\n\n根据**情绪控制**规则：亏损后24h不开仓、冲动等10分钟。这次交易是否在冷静判断后执行？\n\n---\n\n### 📊 持仓更新草案\n\n| 股票 | 数量 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| ORCL | 200 | 持有中 |\n| NVDA | 100 | 持有中 |\n| AMZN | 10 | 持有中 |\n| **BABA** | **10** | **新增 - 待审核** |\n| 国债 | - | 68% |\n| 现金 | - | ~1% |\n\n---\n\n**决定：⏸️ 暂记 | 需补充信息**\n\n请回复买入价格和挂单类型，我完成审查并更新 MEMORY.md。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":10671,"output":582,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11253,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771984363863}}
