{"type":"message","id":"1338dffc","parentId":"c33616d3","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:55:58.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user's message is asking about a memory_search error. It appears they're asking me about a previous memory_search error that occurred when I tried to search for \"BABA 阿里巴巴 交易规则\". The error was about missing API keys for search providers.\n\nThis is a technical question about why memory_search failed. I should explain what happened and provide alternative approaches since API keys aren't configured for memory search.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>对的，刚才 memory_search 报错了。\n\n**问题**：你还没有配置搜索用的 API key。错误提示显示需要配置 openai/google/voyage 中至少一个提供商的 key。\n\n**替代方案**：\n\n1. **直接读取 MEMORY.md**：我直接用 `read` 工具读，刚才已经读到了\n   - ✅ 已获取：交易红线、止损止盈规则\n\n2. **配置搜索 API（可选）**：\n   ```bash\n   openclaw agents add <你的agent_id>\n   # 然后按提示添加 openai/google 等 key\n   ```\n\n**现在的情况是**：我用 `read` 直接读 MEMORY.md 就可以了，搜索功能暂时不用也行。\n\n---\n\n回到你的 BABA 交易——请告诉我：\n- **买入价格**？\n- **限价单还是市价单**？\n\n这样我能完成审查。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":10720,"output":258,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":10978,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771984554595}}
