{"type":"message","id":"5109478b","parentId":"6339c612","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:56:46.479Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what memory_search does. Let me explain clearly and concisely.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>memory_search 是**语义搜索**——它用向量相似度查找 MEMORY.md 和相关文件中的内容。\n\n---\n\n**举例**：\n\n你说\"**BABA 交易**\"，搜索会找到：\n- \"交易红线\"\n- \"买入规则\"\n- \"止损止盈规则\"\n\n即使这些词不完全匹配，AI 也能理解语义关联。\n\n---\n\n**对比**：\n\n| 工具 | 方式 | 用例 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `read` | 直接读取完整文件 | 我知道文件路径，想看全部内容 |\n| `memory_search` | 语义检索片段 | 我不确定相关内容在哪，需要 AI 帮我找 |\n\n---\n\n**你的情况**：搜索报错是因为缺少 API key，但我直接用 `read` 读到了 MEMORY.md，所以不影响交易审查。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":10960,"output":186,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771984603168}}
