{"type":"message","id":"2ca23e60","parentId":"d473b2b9","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:57:27.736Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about memory_search and whether it queries a SQLite-based local memory vector database. Let me explain how it works based on the context I have.\n\nFrom the earlier error message, it seems like memory_search requires external API keys (openai/google/voyage), so it's not using a purely local SQLite database. However, the user mentioned something about `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` in the MEMORY.md file.\n\nLet me check what I know:\n1. The HEARTBEAT.md mentions `memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` for updating search index\n2. MEMORY.md mentions the same thing\n3. The error message says it needs API keys for openai/google/voyage\n\nSo it seems like:\n- There might be a local SQLite database for memory\n- But the semantic search (memory_search) might be using external embedding APIs to do vector search\n\nI should be honest about what I know and don't know based on the documents I've read. I don't have full technical details about the implementation, just what I've seen in the files.\n\nLet me give a helpful but accurate answer.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>从我看到的内容来看，**部分相关但不完全是**：\n\n---\n\n**实际架构（据 MEMORY.md 和报错信息）**：\n\n```\nMEMORY.md / memory/*.md  ──►  sync-to-sqlite.sh  ──►  SQLite 索引\n                                      │\n                                      ▼\n                              向量搜索需要外部 API\n                              (openai/google/voyage)\n```\n\n---\n\n**关键点**：\n\n1. **SQLite 存储**：`memory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh` 把 markdown 文件同步到 SQLite，建立**倒排索引**\n2. **向量搜索需要外部 API**：报错显示需要 openai/google/voyage 的 key，说明**语义向量化**依赖云端\n3. **纯文本搜索可能本地**：如果只是关键词匹配，可能 SQLite 就够；但语义理解需要 embedding API\n\n---\n\n**你的情况**：\n\n你现在的问题是**没有配置 embedding API key**，所以语义搜索走不通。\n- 临时方案：用 `read` 直接读文件 ✅\n- 长期方案：配置 `openai` 或 `voyage` 的 key（`openclaw agents add`）\n\n需要我帮你配置吗？还是先用 `read` 解决当前需求？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":11199,"output":475,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11674,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771984641514}}
{"type":"message","id":"f793fb7c","parentId":"2ca23e60","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:58:48.298Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Wed 2026-02-25 09:58 GMT+8] 语义理解需要 embedding API，但是这个需要 配置 openai 或 voyage 的 key（openclaw agents add） ， 是要收费的吗？\n[message_id: 58c7e183-ee08-4048-ab88-c469e24fe1fa]"}],"timestamp":1771984728297}}
{"type":"message","id":"32d044a5","parentId":"f793fb7c","timestamp":"2026-02-25T01:58:55.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问配置 openai 或 voyage 的 key 是否要收费。这是关于 API 成本的问题。\n\n是的，这些 API 通常是收费的：\n- OpenAI API：按 token 计费\n- Voyage AI：嵌入模型按 token 或请求计费\n\n我需要诚实地回答这个问题，并给出一些替代方案。\n\n替代方案：\n1. 本地嵌入模型（如 Ollama 提供的本地嵌入）\n2. 免费的 Hugging Face 模型\n3. 或者直接使用文件读取（read）来替代搜索\n\n不过我需要确认一下 OpenClaw 是否支持本地嵌入或其他免费方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>**是的，这些 API 是收费的。**\n\n---\n\n### 💰 典型费用\n\n| 服务商 | 计费方式 | 大概价格 |\n|--------|----------|----------|\n| **OpenAI** (text-embedding-3-small) | 按 token | $0.02 / 1M tokens |\n| **Voyage** | 按 token | 稍贵一点 |\n| **Google** (Gemini embedding) | 按 token | 有免费额度 |\n\n---\n\n### 🆓 免费替代方案\n\n**方案一：纯 SQLite（你已经有了）**\n```\nmemory-index/sync-to-sqlite.sh  # 建倒排索引\n```\n- **优点**：本地、免费、足够快\n- **缺点**：只能关键词匹配，**没有语义理解**\n\n**方案二：Ollama 本地嵌入（如果 OpenClaw 支持）**\n- 用你本机的 `llama` 或 `nomic-embed-text`\n- 完全免费、离线运行\n- 不确定当前版本是否支持\n\n---\n\n### 💡 建议\n\n**现阶段**：先用 `read` 直接读 MEMORY.md，交易审查不受影响。\n\n**如果你想省钱**：保持现状，需要搜索时用 `read` + `grep`。\n\n**如果你想要语义搜索**：配置 OpenAI key（有免费额度 $5）或者等 Ollama 本地嵌入支持。\n\n你愿意付这个费用吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":11534,"output":417,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11951,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771984728298}}
