{"type":"message","id":"4762fb20","parentId":"5ad4cc8e","timestamp":"2026-02-25T02:11:28.247Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just typed \"1\" which seems to be a response to my previous message, but I haven't sent my response yet. Let me provide my answer about sub-agents.\n\nLooking at the context, the user seems to be asking about where sub-agents are stored/located. Let me clarify this based on my knowledge of OpenClaw.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>Sub-agent 的位置通常在：\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/agents/\n├── main/           ← 你当前的 agent\n├── <其他agent>/    ← 独立子 agent\n```\n\n它们**不在 workspace 里**，因为：\n- Workspace 是**你**的工作目录（项目文件、笔记）\n- Agent 目录是**系统配置**（prompt 模板、权限、API keys）\n\n---\n\n**你想查看/管理子 agent？**\n\n```bash\n# 列出所有 agent\nopenclaw agents list\n\n# 查看详情\nopenclaw agents status <agent_id>\n\n# 查看当前有哪些可用（spawnable）\nopenclaw agents list --spawnable\n```\n\n---\n\n**你问这个是因为想：**\n- A) 自定义某个子 agent？\n- B) 把 agent 配置放进 workspace 备份？\n- C) 单纯好奇架构？\n\n告诉我目的，我给你具体命令。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":12314,"output":261,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12575,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771985475909}}
