{"type":"message","id":"285cec16","parentId":"544631ef","timestamp":"2026-02-25T03:28:17.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the memory system for sub-agents vs the main workspace memory. Let me explain the architecture:\n\n1. **Main workspace memory** (what we've been working with):\n   - `MEMORY.md` - long-term curated memory\n   - `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md` - daily logs\n   - `SOUL.md`, `USER.md`, etc.\n   - This is in `/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace/`\n\n2. **Sub-agent memory**:\n   - When you spawn a sub-agent with `sessions_spawn`, it creates an isolated session\n   - Each session can have its own context/memory\n   - The sub-agent doesn't automatically have access to the workspace MEMORY.md\n   - Sub-agents can read/write to the workspace if given permission, but by default they might be isolated\n\nLet me check the runtime info and think about this:\n- Runtime shows `repo=/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace`\n- Sub-agents are spawned sessions\n\nThe key distinction:\n- **Workspace memory**: Persistent, your files (MEMORY.md, etc.)\n- **Sub-agent memory**: Typically session-scoped, temporary, lives for the duration of the task\n\nWhen a sub-agent finishes, its memory can optionally be:\n- Summarized back to the parent\n- Written to the workspace\n- Or just discarded\n\nI should explain this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>是的，架构不同：\n\n---\n\n## memory 对比\n\n| 特性 | Workspace Memory | Sub-agent Memory |\n|------|------------------|------------------|\n| **位置** | `/workspace/MEMORY.md` | 会话独立（内存/临时） |\n| **持久化** | ✅ 文件存储，长期保留 | ⚠️ 会话结束即回收 |\n| **访问范围** | 主 agent + 所有子 agent | 仅当前子 agent |\n| **用途** | 你的账本、规则、人设 | 单次任务上下文 |\n| **同步** | SQLite 索引、可搜索 | 通常不索引 |\n\n---\n\n## 工作方式\n\n当你 `sessions_spawn` 一个子 agent：\n\n```\n父会话 (main)\n    ├── 读取 MEMORY.md 获取背景\n    ├── 派生子 agent\n    │       └── 子 agent 开始：空上下文 或 你给的 task\n    │       └── 子 agent 干活...\n    │       └── 子 agent 完成 → 返回结果\n    └── 父会话收到结果，更新 MEMORY.md\n```\n\n**关键点**：\n- 子 agent **默认不自动读取** MEMORY.md\n- 如果需要，你要在 `task` 里告诉他\"去 read MEMORY.md\"\n- 子 agent 的成果可以写回 workspace（通过文件写入）\n\n---\n\n**实际例子**：\n\n```javascript\n// 你调用\nsessions_spawn({\n  task: \"帮我分析这只股票，参考交易规则\",\n  // 子 agent 不知道规则在哪！\n})\n\n// 正确做法\nsessions_spawn({\n  task: \"先读取 /workspace/MEMORY.md 的交易红线，然后分析...\"\n})\n```\n\n---\n\n**总结**：Workspace memory 是**持久数据库**，Sub-agent memory 是**临时工作区**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":15906,"output":653,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16559,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771990084564}}
