{"type":"message","id":"a57f9cc6","parentId":"ef7e0136","timestamp":"2026-02-25T03:31:16.359Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking whether it's reasonable for sub-agents to have their own independent memory, separate from the workspace memory. This is a design/architecture question.\n\nLet me think about the pros and cons:\n\n**Pros of sub-agent having independent memory:**\n1. Isolation - tasks don't pollute each other's context\n2. Parallel work - multiple sub-agents can work simultaneously without conflicts\n3. Clean slate - each task starts fresh, no baggage from previous tasks\n4. Security - sensitive task data doesn't persist unnecessarily\n\n**Cons:**\n1. No learning - sub-agent can't accumulate knowledge across tasks\n2. Repetition - same context needs to be loaded each time\n3. \"Memory loss\" - after task completes, insights are lost unless explicitly written back\n\n**The OpenClaw approach:**\n- Workspace = persistent memory (your stuff)\n- Sub-agent = ephemeral per-session memory\n- Results written back = persistence mechanism\n\nI should answer: Yes, it's reasonable for the architecture, but with caveats about when to use workspace vs sub-agent memory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>是的，**合理，且必要**。\n\n---\n\n## 为什么子 agent 需要独立 memory？\n\n### 1. **隔离性** (Isolation)\n```\n子 agent A：分析股票 → 错误结论\n子 agent B：分析财报 → 完全独立\n```\n- A 的错误不会污染 B\n- 任务失败不会留下烂摊子\n\n### 2. **并行安全**\n```\n同时 spawn 3 个子 agent 分析不同股票\n```\n- 各自独立内存，互不干扰\n- 如果共享 memory，会互相覆盖/混乱\n\n### 3. **沙盒效应**\n```\n子 agent fetch 可疑网页 → 本地隔离\n```\n- 风险 contained in session\n- 结束后清理，不留痕迹\n\n---\n\n## 但带来的问题\n\n| 问题 | 解决方案 |\n|------|----------|\n| 每次启动空白 | `task` 中明确写入所需背景 |\n| 跨任务无记忆 | 重要结果显式写回 `workspace/` |\n| 重复加载上下文 | `MEMORY.md` 作为\"冷存储\"按需读取 |\n\n---\n\n## 对比设计\n\n| 架构 | 场景 |\n|------|------|\n| **共享 memory** (无隔离) | 单任务、串行、完全信任 |\n| **独立 memory** (OpenClaw) | 多任务、并行、需要审查 |\n\n**你的场景**（投资监督）：\n- 分析某只股票 → spawn 子 agent ✅ 合理\n- 子 agent 出错 → 主 agent 审查后决定 ✅ 安全\n- 关键结论 → 写回 `MEMORY.md` ✅ 持久化\n\n**结论**：独立 memory 是 feature，不是 bug。它强制你**显式管理**什么该留、什么该扔。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":16340,"output":586,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16926,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771990258320}}
