{"type":"message","id":"d88398d8","parentId":"aeaf8efe","timestamp":"2026-02-25T03:32:37.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HEARTBEAT 检查 - 没有新待办事项。BABA 交易已处理完成，审查通过。现在回复用户关于 workspace memory 的定义问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n---\n\n## 对的，可以这样理解\n\n| 层级 | 对应 | 类比 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Workspace** | 主 agent 的 memory | 你的\"外脑\" |\n| **Sub-agent** (spawn) | 临时 consultant | 请的专家 |\n\n---\n\n**更准确的说法**：\n\n```\n主 agent (me)\n    ├── 当前会话内存 (上下文)\n    └── 显式读取 ← Workspace/MEMORY.md\n\n子 agent (spawn)\n    ├── 当前会话内存 (独立)\n    └── 可能需要显式读取 Workspace\n```\n\n---\n\n**关键区别**：\n\n| | 主 agent | Sub-agent |\n|--|----------|-----------|\n| Workspace 访问 | 默认有 | 默认有（权限） |\n| 自动加载 MEMORY | ❌ 需要 `read` | ❌ 需要 `read` |\n| 会话结束后的记忆 | 只有写回的文件保留 | 完全消失 |\n\n---\n\n**所以**：\n\n```\nWorkspace/MEMORY.md = 持久化知识库\n子 agent = 带沙盒的临时工作单元\n```\n\n你的账本就放在 workspace，主 agent 把关，子 agent 干活。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":16820,"output":285,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17105,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771990349940}}
