{"type":"message","id":"30c354d2","parentId":"64a2ed80","timestamp":"2026-02-25T03:43:23.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The agents_list shows that only \"main\" is available and it's not configured. The user is asking about \"/agents\" command - this might be an OpenClaw CLI command. Let me show them what agents are available and explain how to configure them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>当前可用 agents：\n\n| ID | 配置状态 | 说明 |\n|----|----------|------|\n| `main` | ❌ 未配置 | 默认主 agent |\n\n---\n\n**可用命令**：\n\n```bash\n# 查看详细配置\nopenclaw agents status main\n\n# 配置 agent（添加 API key）\nopenclaw agents add main\n# 然后按提示选择 provider（openai/google 等）\n\n# 配置完成后重启\nopenclaw gateway restart\n```\n\n---\n\n**当前限制**：\n\n目前只有 `main` agent，没有独立的子 agent 预设。\n\n如果你想创建**专用子 agent**（比如交易分析专用），需要：\n1. 配置 `main` 先（添加 embedding/模型 API）\n2. 或者手动创建 agent 配置\n\n**要现在配置吗？** 还是先用 `main` 的 `sessions_spawn` 功能？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":17153,"output":241,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17394,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771990993906}}
