{"type":"message","id":"cb5fcee4","parentId":"bafe5afb","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:19:23.046Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The agents_list only shows \"main\" agent, and it's not configured. The user mentioned \"stock sub-agent\" but there's no stock-specific agent listed.\n\nLooking at MEMORY.md, it mentions:\n```\n## 🔧 Skills\nstock-advisor | trading-supervisor\n```\n\nThese are probably skills, not sub-agents. Let me check if there are any sessions running or if there's a specific agent the user expects to exist.\n\nThe user is frustrated that something they expected to be there (stock sub-agent) is not working. I should:\n1. Acknowledge the confusion\n2. Clarify that the \"stock-advisor\" listed in MEMORY.md is a *skill*, not a sub-agent\n3. Explain what would need to be done to actually create/use a stock sub-agent\n\nLet me be helpful and not defensive here.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>澄清一下，你是对的——**workspace 是主 agent 的持久存储**。\n\n关于\"股票子 agent\"的问题：\n\n---\n\n## 现状检查\n\n**当前可用 agents**：\n```\nrequester: main\nallowAny: false\nagents: [ { id: \"main\", configured: false } ]\n```\n\n**只有 `main`，没有 `stock-advisor` 或其他 agent。**\n\n---\n\n## MEMORY.md 里的 `stock-advisor | trading-supervisor` 是什么？\n\n这些是 **Skills（技能）**，不是独立的 sub-agents：\n```\n## 🔧 Skills\nstock-advisor | trading-supervisor\n```\n\n含义：我（主 agent）可以通过这些技能帮你，但**不是独立的子 agent**。\n\n---\n\n## 你想要什么？\n\n| 选项 | 含义 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **A) Stock skill 生效** | 主 agent 使用 stock-advisor skill | ✅ 应该已生效，我用它审查了 BABA 交易 |\n| **B) 独立 Stock 子 agent** | spawn 一个专门看股票的 agent | ❌ 不存在，需要创建 |\n| **C) Skill 没工作** | 审查 BABA 时规则检查没生效？ | ❓ 需你确认 |\n\n---\n\n**请确认**：你期望的\"股票子 agent 生效\"是指？\n1. **Spawn 一个独立 agent** 让它专门监控股票？\n2. **Stock skill 在审查交易时没生效**？\n\n我需要知道你想要什么，才能解决\"没生效\"的问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":18924,"output":495,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19