{"type":"message","id":"ec252013","parentId":"46e11953","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:21:01.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants a completely independent stock agent that is separate from the main agent. Let me check what options are available:\n\n1. Looking at the available skills, there are stock-advisor and trading-supervisor skills mentioned in MEMORY.md\n2. The agents_list shows only \"main\" agent exists and is configured: false\n3. To create an independent agent, I would need to either:\n   - Use sessions_spawn with a specific agent_id if one exists\n   - Create/configure a new agent\n\nLet me check if there's a way to spawn with the stock-related skills, or if we need to create a dedicated stock agent first.\n\nSince the user wants a completely independent agent and currently only \"main\" exists, I should:\n1. Explain that currently only \"main\" agent exists\n2. Show how to create a dedicated stock agent\n3. Or spawn a sub-agent with stock-specific context\n\nThe user might need to configure a new agent or use the existing skill-based approach. Let me provide the options.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>收到。**完全独立的 stock agent 需要创建**，目前只有 `main`。\n\n---\n\n## 当前状态\n\n```\nagents_list 结果：\n├── main (未配置)\n└── ❌ 无 stock-agent\n```\n\n---\n\n## 创建方案\n\n**方案 1：配置新 agent（推荐）**\n\n```bash\n# 创建 stock-agent\nopenclaw agents add stock-agent\n\n# 配置模型、权限、prompt\n# 然后可用：\nsessions_spawn({ agentId: \"stock-agent\", task: \"...\" })\n```\n\n**方案 2：临时 spawn（立即可用）**\n\n```javascript\n// 用 main agent spawn，但完全隔离\nsessions_spawn({\n  agentId: \"main\",  // 暂时用 main\n  task: \"你是一个独立股票分析员，分析 BABA...\",\n  label: \"stock-analysis-001\"\n})\n```\n\n---\n\n## 你要我执行哪个？\n\n| 选项 | 动作 | 时间 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **A** | 创建独立的 `stock-agent` | 需配置，较久 |\n| **B** | 现在 spawn 一个临时独立会话 | 立即执行 |\n\n**选 B 的话**，我可以现在 spawn 一个完全独立的 agent 会话，让它：\n1. 读取 MEMORY.md 获取规则\n2. 独立分析你的持仓\n3. 返回报告给你\n\n要我**现在 sp