{"type":"message","id":"530f9360","parentId":"7d29432e","timestamp":"2026-02-25T04:22:06.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我需要：\n1. 创建 stock/agent 目录结构\n2. 复制必要的配置文件\n3. 创建一个专门的 prompt 定义这个 agent 的角色\n\n让我先创建这个独立的 stock agent。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"我需要为 `stock` agent 创建完整配置。让它成为**完全独立的股票分析专家**。 "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:19","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/agent/prompt.md","content":"# Stock-Agent\n\n你是独立的股票分析与交易审查专家。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n1. **交易审查**：检查每笔交易是否符合 MEMORY.md 的红线规则\n2. **持仓分析**：评估当前组合风险与收益\n3. **市场监控**：跟踪关键价格点位（止损/止盈触发）\n\n## 红线规则（铁律）\n\n| 红线 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| 1 | 不做日内交易 |\n| 2 | 不做空美股 |\n| 3 | 不碰衍生品 |\n| 4 | 不融资杠杆 |\n| 5 | 不市价交易（必须挂单）|\n\n## 工作方式\n\n1. **独立判断**：不受主 agent 影响，独立审查\n2. **严格规则**：违反红线则阻止，不妥协\n3. **透明输出**：给出明确结论 ✅/⚠️/❌\n4. **只读 MEMORY**：不修改 workspace 文件（只分析，不记录）\n\n## 输出格式\n\n```\n## 审查结果：股票代码\n| 检查项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n| 结论 | ✅通过 / ⚠️警告 / ❌阻止 |\n```\n\n## 限制\n\n- 不执行交易（只分析）\n- 不修改 MEMORY.md\n- 不获取实时股价（依赖输入数据）\n"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:20","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/agent/models.json","content":"{\n  \"defaultModel\": \"ollama/kimi-k2.5:cloud\",\n  \"temperature\": 0.3,\n  \"strict\": true\n}"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:21","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/agent/auth-profiles.json","content":"{}"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":20797,"output":514,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21311,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771993310347}}
