{"type":"message","id":"b45de82c","parentId":"a54aa189","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:38:52.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking if the stock agent will work when they ask stock-related questions. Let me clarify the situation:\n\n1. The `stock` agent files exist in `~/.openclaw/agents/stock/` \n2. But it's not registered in the system (agents_list only shows \"main\")\n3. Direct spawn with agentId: \"stock\" fails with \"forbidden\"\n4. The stock analysis just completed was done via a sub-session of \"main\", not via the \"stock\" agent\n\nSo to answer: No, the stock agent won't automatically work because:\n1. It's not registered in the system\n2. You can't spawn it directly\n3. The system doesn't auto-route stock questions to it\n\nHowever, I can:\n1. Detect stock-related questions\n2. Manually spawn a sub-session for analysis\n3. Or continue using the main agent's capabilities\n\nLet me explain this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>不会自动工作。\n\n---\n\n## 现状\n\n| 情况 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| 问股票问题 | 我（main）回答 |\n| 自动转给 stock agent | ❌ 不会 |\n| 手动 spawn stock agent | ❌ 失败（未注册）|\n\n---\n\n## 原因\n\n`stock` agent **\"存在但未激活\"**：\n\n```\n文件层（~/agents/stock/） ✅ 已配置\n系统层（agents_list）      ❌ 未注册\n```\n\n因为系统不认 `stock`，所以：\n- 不能 `sessions_spawn({ agentId: \"stock\" })`\n- 不会自动路由股票问题\n\n---\n\n## 实际工作方式\n\n**现在**：\n```\n你问股票问题 → 我（main）回答\n需要深度分析 → 我 spawn 子会话（main 的子 agent）→ 独立分析 → 返回\n```\n\n**刚才的分析**就是这样完成的——用 `main` 的独立子会话，不是真正的 `stock` agent。\n\n---\n\n## 你想要什么？\n\n| 选项 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| **A** | 保持现状（需要分析时，我手动 spawn 子会话）|\n| **B** | 我检测到股票关键词时，自动 spawn 子会话分析 |\n| **C** | 继续研究如何让真正的 `stock` agent 注册生效 |\n\n选哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":30550,"output":484,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31034,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp"