{"type":"message","id":"6fde7cc0","parentId":"8bd16f7c","timestamp":"2026-02-25T05:41:38.519Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Interesting! The filesystem shows both `main` and `stock` directories exist, but `agents_list` only returns `main`. So the agent files are there but the system isn't registering/picking up `stock`.\n\nThe user says they can switch agent, which suggests there might be a way to do this that I'm not seeing. Let me check if there's an `openclaw` CLI command to interact with agents, or if I can try to spawn stock again now that the files are confirmed to exist.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>文件确实存在：\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/agents/\n├── main/   ✅\n└── stock/  ✅\n```\n\n但 `agents_list` 只返回 `main`——**系统没扫描到 stock**。\n\n---\n\n你说能切换 agent？用什么方式？\n\n我这边：\n- `agents_list` → 只显示 `main`\n- `sessions_spawn({ agentId: \"stock\" })` → `forbidden`\n\n**可能情况**：\n1. 你用 CLI 命令看到的？（`openclaw agents list` 输出不同？）\n2. 有缓存/延迟，需要再重启？\n3. 配置路径不对？\n\n**你能截图或贴一下**你怎么看到 stock-agent 已注册的吗？这样我能对齐信息。\n\n或者你现在试试：\n```\nopenclaw agents list\n```\n输出是什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":31115,"output":277,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31392,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771998092932}}
