{"type":"message","id":"e347b663","parentId":"3cb5cbaa","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:42:23.342Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the config is updated now. Let me verify the final state of the workspace separation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>✅ workspace 分离完成\n\n---\n\n## 当前状态\n\n| Agent | Workspace 路径 | 状态 |\n|-------|----------------|------|\n| `main` | `~/.openclaw/workspace/` | ✅ 共享目录（原始） |\n| `stock` | `~/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace/` | ✅ 独立目录 |\n\n---\n\n## 配置信息\n\n**openclaw.json 已更新**：\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"main\": { \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace\" },\n  \"stock\": { \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace\" }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 各 workspace 内容\n\n**Main workspace**（共用）：\n- AGENTS.md, MEMORY.md, SOUL.md, HEARTBEAT.md, USER.md\n- memory/, memory-index/\n- skills/, blog/, 其他项目文件\n\n**Stock workspace**（独立）：\n- MEMORY.md（已同步最新 BABA 交易）\n- SOUL.md, HEARTBEAT.md, USER.md\n- memory/, memory-index/\n\n---\n\n## 使用方式\n\n| 场景 | 读取的 MEMORY |\n|------|--------------|\n| 我在 main 回答 | `~/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md` |\n| Stock agent 回答 | `~/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace/MEMORY.md` |\n\n**注意**：两个 MEMORY.md 现在**各自独立**。如果修改持仓，需要**手动同步**到另一个 agent。\n\n---\n\n下一步：\n- 在网页端切换到 stock agent\n- stock agent 会使用它自己的 workspace"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":37778,"output":366,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772001736126}}
