{"type":"message","id":"9f051779","parentId":"5b0b0f33","timestamp":"2026-02-25T07:02:25.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The config is now correct. The agents.list has both main and stock. But agents_list is not showing stock. This might be a known issue or there's something else wrong.\n\nLet me provide a summary to the user - the config is now correct according to the documentation. But there's still an issue with stock not appearing in agents_list.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>配置已按官方文档修复，但 `stock` agent 仍未被系统识别。\n\n---\n\n## 当前配置状态 (`openclaw.json`)\n\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": { ... },\n  \"list\": [\n    { \"id\": \"main\", \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace\" },\n    { \"id\": \"stock\", \"workspace\": \"/Users/hope/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace\" }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**✅ 符合官方文档结构**\n\n---\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/agents/\n├── main/\n│   ├── agent/      ✅ (已配置)\n│   ├── sessions/   ✅\n│   └── workspace/  ✅ (已建立)\n└── stock/\n    ├── agent/      ✅ (config.json, prompt.md, models.json, auth-profiles.json)\n    └── workspace/  ✅ (MEMORY.md, SOUL.md 等)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 问题\n\n| 检查 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| `agents_list` API | ❌ 只返回 `main` |\n| 网页端 UI | ❓ 待你确认是否能看到 stock |\n\n**可能原因**：\n1. `stock/agent/` 目录权限问题（已修复 `chmod 700`）\n2. 网页端路由绑定（bindings）需要单独配置\n3. Gateway 启动时需要特定的 agent 发现机制\n\n---\n\n**请检查网页端**：\n- 是否能看到 `stock` agent？\n- 切换到它能正常工作吗？\n\n如果网页端能看到但 API 看不到，可能是运行时缓存问题。如果都看不到，可能需要 CLI 命令显式注册：\n```bash\nopenclaw agents add stock --workspace ~/.openclaw/agents/stock/workspace\n```\n\n你的网页端现在是什么状态？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":44996,"output":450,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772002930523}}
